item.dc:creator: @Javacisnotrecognized _^_
item.description:
@Javacisnotrecognized wrote:

Clients are for playing on servers. The client is YOUR end of the game. It is responsible for drawing the images on the screen that make you realize your playing the game. It also notes when you click or type into it, so it can give text and other information to the server, so that the server can update the game for all the other clients connected to it.
